{"tid":1441363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"講廣傳 前線黨衛軍（警察）已打白粉針 所以上前打得好high","createTime":"2019-08-10T15:50:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T01:45:36.000Z","uid":24814,"like":446,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"70a24939aceb37c640a89db93a0b45a3ca0bee7c","tid":1441363,"uid":24814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:50:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tri2Thn.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftri2Thn.gif&h=42dfd342&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oqwcv4b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOqwcv4b.jpg&h=a651095b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聽內鬼講前線popo好多都打咗白粉針<br />\n大sir派咗一人一支 上頭默許 個個上哂電先出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打針完之後 要搵人出火先冷靜到 所以呢排先咁癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請文宣組廣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85df15735d98e9de48e36522acad267bb97eadea","tid":1441363,"uid":24814,"like":56,"dislike":1,"score":55,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:54:17.000Z","msg":"連日嘅示威重打遊擊 個個popo都好攰<br />\n大sir就一人畀咗一支針 話打咗佢就有精神<br />\n聽講係強國特務暗中畀佢哋嘅"},{"pid":"a7faa21dec5b181438278300e838b9c516581a13","tid":1441363,"uid":24814,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:58:49.000Z","msg":"使用初有感覺愉快安靜，無法集中精神，會產生夢幻現象(幻覺)。吸食之後的12小時，身體由於得不到麻醉劑而不能正常運作，即時出現緊張、無法入睡、出汗、腸胃不適、四肢疼痛及痙攣等斷癮症狀。這症狀持續三到五天。濫用越久，斷癮症狀越長。過量使用造成急性中毒，症狀包括昏睡、呼吸抑制、低血壓、瞳孔變小。"},{"pid":"ee67369d95f949a68a78e6d96116070c15f465d5","tid":1441363,"uid":24814,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:01:24.000Z","msg":"有內鬼講可能係氯胺酮針唔係白粉 但一定有人畀針佢哋打"},{"pid":"2e9b876ee87c86b01c4f2b81a0d2c9bf5d956b36","tid":1441363,"uid":24814,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:03:08.000Z","msg":"注射低劑量的K他命，能夠快速改善憂鬱症，藥效能維持數天至兩週[18]；未來K他命或類似K他命的藥品有機會成為合法的憂鬱症用藥。"},{"pid":"e3e1cab30a3356bc10d4b862aa124a5f150f3ed6","tid":1441363,"uid":24814,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:04:43.000Z","msg":"過量施用氯胺酮會產生分離性幻覺，並會引致後遺症及腦部永久損害。氯胺酮曾在世界各地的夜店，如舞廳、迪斯可、狂野派對場所內被人使用，使用後會使人對周圍環境失去警覺性。"},{"pid":"98fff934809d73277ec869654cd786536b426c4b","tid":1441363,"uid":24814,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:08:34.000Z","msg":"PoPo打咗針 上頭日日洗腦講示威者係惡人 曱甴<br />\n當咗係真 白粉針畀佢哋嘅幻覺係咁 所以起勢咁打"},{"pid":"058aefc06fe9cce698465802e6e54add70c8f6e1","tid":1441363,"uid":185960,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:10:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1LFMotPfcLCi5MXxioVQX2E32ovPvizhH?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fdrive%2Ffolders%2F1LFMotPfcLCi5MXxioVQX2E32ovPvizhH%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=y7g0wjbeyFmnVC7InFCgMmINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=c1146e1c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1LFMotPfcLCi5MXxioVQX2E32ovPvizhH?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n[文宣］黑白大字報 政權罪行 遍地開花<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1360258\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1360258</a><br />\n<br />\n文宣就係做比藍絲、港豬<br />\n做比自己人睇有撚用！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ffec40ea95054ae90acd8af7682650e374e26c1","tid":1441363,"uid":252973,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:12:03.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00082eebddd35ae0a0465819577eefb03ef35b65","tid":1441363,"uid":269578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:12:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6043f7091c85e5fb4660f820b649756a583e765","tid":1441363,"uid":176166,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:12:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"